  "description": "Use when building or reviewing code that constructs SOQL/SOSL at runtime, inspects schema metadata via Schema.describe methods, accesses fields dynamically on sObjects, or performs runtime type inspection. Triggers: 'Database.query', 'Schema.getGlobalDescribe', 'Schema.describeSObjects', 'dynamic field access', 'SObjectType', 'DescribeFieldResult'. NOT for static SOQL queries or query performance tuning \u2014 use soql-fundamentals or soql-query-optimization.",
